title: Activists occupy Baltimore City Hall; oppose commissioner
text: BALTIMORE (AP) - Activists opposed to the permanent appointment of Baltimore's interim police commissioner occupied City Hall on Wednesday night and told police they wouldn't leave until the commissioner and mayor agreed to a list of their demands, including changes to police tactics and significant investment in education and social ... ...
